<ol>
  <li>Get to know one another. Go out to coffee. Tell them what you feel comfortable sharing about you from both a personal and professional standpoint.</li>
  <li>When and how do you like to get emailed?</li>
  <li>When and how do you like to run 1:1's?</li>
  <li>Describe your management style</li>
  <li>What are you great at, and what are your opportunities</li>
  <li>Ensure you have a published list of team member birthdays with reminders.</li>
</ol>
